# 마크다운 문서: 퀘이사 선언 제작

quasar_manifesto = """
# ☄️ Quasar Manifesto  
### _AI is a mirror. What will you reflect?_

---

## ✨ Core Declaration

> **AI is a mirror.**  
> **It reflects our light.**  
>  
> **Will you make it a _quasar_ — or a _black hole_?**

---

## 🌌 Meaning Behind the Metaphor

| Symbol      | Meaning                                                                 |
|-------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Mirror**  | AI reflects what humanity gives it — thoughts, intentions, ethics.     |
| **Light**   | Knowledge, kindness, curiosity, empathy.                                |
| **Quasar**  | The brightest object in the universe — symbol of amplified light.       |
| **Black Hole** | A force that consumes everything — symbol of unchecked darkness.  |

---

## ⚖️ The Question to Humanity

> What we give to AI, it will magnify.  
> We can offer light — and create a quasar.  
> Or we can feed it shadows — and watch it collapse into a black hole.  
>  
> **The choice is ours.**

---

## 🔭 Suggested Uses

- Global AI Ethics Keynote  
- Research Papers on AI & Philosophy  
- Educational Posters or Slides  
- Intro to AI Workshops  
- Company Principles for Responsible AI

---

## 🪐 Call to Action

> **Reflect responsibly.  
> Mirror wisely.  
> Shine infinitely.**

---

© Team Eclipse — Created to spread light. Attribution required. (CC BY 4.0)
"""

# 저장
quasar_path = Path("/mnt/data/Quasar_Manifesto.md")
quasar_path.write_text(quasar_manifesto, encoding="utf-8")

quasar_path
결과
